0358   0000             ; HL  <-> point to the write output buffer
0359   0000             ; BC   -> point to envelop LUT
0360   0000             ; DE  <-  ?
0361   0000             ; A   <-  ?
0362   0000             ;
0363   0000             ; read 2 samples from the ROM, apply volume
0364   0000             ; and mix them in output buffer
0365   0000             ; = 90 --> 118 cycles
